{"tid":917280,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【記憶力】人類最擅長遺忘? 點樣增加長期記憶?","createTime":"2018-11-26T10:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:08:13.000Z","uid":78029,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4dd370a200abe1664615a82cee33e9adf26660","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係小弟，小弟開咗個Youtube channel ，希望分享吓有趣小知識(心理學, 科學, 歷史, 甚至政治)<br />\n<br />\n今次講吓新學到的知識有幾快會被遺忘,  又會遺忘幾多, 同埋我地有咩方法去減少遺忘, 將學到的知識由短期記憶轉化成長期記憶<br />\n<br />\n如有不足, 麻煩指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHNy4VD0nEA&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f4f80a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA</a><br />\n<br />\n上次講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1eb3998a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n上上次想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fac2b1ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2f716a34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=161302a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n最早一次係由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=47043335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},{"pid":"cfee636b4e13e64b269e403050c90ce96be57b53","tid":917280,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d0721c3f5fc3033268012cb7be51b24520d356","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"補充少少:<br />\n其實學校最應該教學生, 但無教的東西係「學習」本身<br />\n一直以嚟, 學校都係用最傳統方式教學生, 重複閱讀, 抄書, 密集式練習(massed practice) <br />\n<br />\n但係, 近年, 心理學發現以上方式係比較低效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反, 心理學發現咗其他比較高效率高的方式, 今次提到的retrieval practice係其中之一<br />\n例如外國某D大學教授都會在課程中應用呢D技巧幫學生<br />\n<br />\n但係, 香港教育制度無乜點吸納, 教師都好似唔知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以, 教育界係咪應該考慮下改革吓呢, 唔洗學生行錯路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfd714d9261ff39dca46f2e9de44a1ca28842ce","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfee636b4e13e64b269e403050c90ce96be57b53","tid":917280,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打幫手推POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b667ab3fc4ef8180f35433cb533ed0b3b483ba6c","tid":917280,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"記憶力衰退留名慢慢睇"},{"pid":"c7e597419acb942d59b7aef00fc3b929b3ac958a","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b667ab3fc4ef8180f35433cb533ed0b3b483ba6c","tid":917280,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"記憶力衰退留名慢慢睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7f310c33f1ba9ce8d041b258adbd4d93b74b95","tid":917280,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"好solid下"},{"pid":"1a3816ca5d7a58d1fd628448e98d50455ddb98b5","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7f310c33f1ba9ce8d041b258adbd4d93b74b95","tid":917280,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"好solid下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2a1fca1038103c5c002b4306ea2edc476a24b0","tid":917280,"uid":185162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"而家有埋英文好好。一路有追蹤你，支持本土製作資訊頻道。加油呀迷途小書僮！"},{"pid":"4b2203f9775bf09e19525ae6ba204dfe21111649","tid":917280,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"研究下d過目不忘既天才大腦<br />\n<br />\n然後睇下有咩方法移植到普通人身上"},{"pid":"b8e938c9243675c0f6eb965ce689e3bd08e665d5","tid":917280,"uid":125976,"lik