oji\" /> <br />\n其實巴打可能唔係記憶力差, 可能係用錯方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"其實幾灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大記野背野都好差，好輸蝕<br />\n我發覺自己分析同解決問題都比較其他人好，但係讀書唔叻，做野又俾人覺得好似唔上心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望睇完有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8661107698c98869c86ae93c2b3803c58ed9e31","tid":917280,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9cb56dfbe90d07503a207064b586febbc17c2da5","tid":917280,"uid":54153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"睇咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學緊日文，睇文法書同埋背單字都係好快唔記得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日開始試下用recall果個方法溫文法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf846c90539e04af65df48c170f773a88840f1b1","tid":917280,"uid":205065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:52:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1805111534c3144a3808246b2b82220e774a8c74","tid":917280,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:20:19.000Z","msg":"Make It Stick（超牢記憶法）<br />\n<br />\n成本書都係講呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n仲有提及間隔練習、交錯練習<br />\n<br />\n3個方法一齊用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39373a00c63d72c5b09b9e3f2c688ba50e65fdd0","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1805111534c3144a3808246b2b82220e774a8c74","tid":917280,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:20:19.000Z","msg":"Make It Stick（超牢記憶法）<br />\n<br />\n成本書都係講呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n仲有提及間隔練習、交錯練習<br />\n<br />\n3個方法一齊用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime