33e9adf26660","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係小弟，小弟開咗個Youtube channel ，希望分享吓有趣小知識(心理學, 科學, 歷史, 甚至政治)<br />\n<br />\n今次講吓新學到的知識有幾快會被遺忘,  又會遺忘幾多, 同埋我地有咩方法去減少遺忘, 將學到的知識由短期記憶轉化成長期記憶<br />\n<br />\n如有不足, 麻煩指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHNy4VD0nEA&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f4f80a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA</a><br />\n<br />\n上次講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1eb3998a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n上上次想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fac2b1ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2f716a34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=161302a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n最早一次係由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=47043335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"衰野通常記一世"},{"pid":"08e6b5c9a34eb5fecd2f6fc7d0074102901aacf6","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cb56dfbe90d07503a207064b586febbc17c2da5","tid":917280,"uid":54153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"睇咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學緊日文，睇文法書同埋背單字都係好快唔記得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日開始試下用recall果個方法溫文法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:09:27.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背單字言都可以用呢個方法, 唔止學文法可以用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff084f30d87e1ccaa94da3e02c1a2a02fccb74da","tid":917280,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"可唔可以簡單講下方法<br />\n唔想禁入去睇"},{"pid":"6652f4c9ccadf3ca8a2e650ae1bfaf8d32664230","tid":917280,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"G持高質channel，學到好多野<br />\n但聲演方面有待進步<br />\n至少要改善下懶音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cc6a6ad4becc835b99e2681afc2311aeaf932f","tid":917280,"uid":59886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"訓唔夠已經唔洗講唔夠記憶"},{"pid":"329e540fac088d525d070e8b4b3b7779d0a7c574","tid":917280,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,